Silex integration
==================

CalendR is bundled with a Silex integration.

Juste use :

```php

    $app->register(new CalendR\Extension\Silex\Provider\CalendRServiceProvider(), array(
        'calendr.event.providers' => array(
            // Your providers likes 'provider_name' => new YourAwesomeProvider()
        )
    ));

```

To add CalendR support to silex.

You can now use `$app['calendr']` everywhere in your silex app.

If you use twig, the CalendR twig extension will automatically be added to Twig.
